title: LF: Gold-Plat Midlaner for Clash this weekend!
body:
Looking for a Mid lane main, preferably high gold (G2+)to low plat (P4) to play Mid lane for clash this weekend!

Ideally we'll be playing some games beforehand, to see if there is synergy with our team.

We'll be using discord for voice communication

My in game name is "Mangø" just copy&paste it because of alternative characters.
